- Hardcoded UI label/element strings in components.
- Hardcoded success/error/info messages in components.
- Hardcoded log messages in services.
- Hardcoded error messages in middleware.
- Hardcoded API URLs in code.
- Hardcoded database names, schema names, or other config values that come from the API.

