- Import shared components via `import { ComponentName } from '@shared'`.
- Barrel export: `src/shared/index.js` вЂ” ALL shared components MUST be exported here.
- PROHIBITED: Duplicating component logic across modules.

**Current Shared Components:**
- `Button.jsx` вЂ” Multi-variant button.
- `ConfigLayout.jsx` вЂ” Tabbed configuration panel (used by Settings).
- `ConfirmationModal.jsx` вЂ” 3-phase CRUD modal (Confirm в†’ Progress в†’ Summary).
- `ConnectionStatus.jsx` вЂ” Connection status indicator with meta info.
- `CrudSummary.jsx` вЂ” Standalone CRUD summary display.
- `DatabaseManager.jsx` вЂ” Database CRUD operations panel.
- `LoggingConfig.jsx` вЂ” Log configuration component.
- `LogStats.jsx` вЂ” Log statistics display (count, storage, last sync).
